value.text: Not to be confused with Performing arts.

Although the label of this item is plural, this represents the performing art class and not the group of performing arts. The definition of "performing art" is the same as "performing arts" in most languages
Refers broadly to the areas of activity that encompass both performing and visual arts. With reference more narrowly to the fine arts or the fine and decorative arts together, see "art."
